<br>
For the purpose of expanding the minds of our nations citizens to brothers and sisters elsewhere in the Micro-national world.  That both nations will benefit from cultural exchange and friendship.<br>
<br>
Section II<br>
3. We will not reconize or form relations with a nation who is bent on warmongering.  A nation who has performed Terror, hacking, cracking, bombing, or has employed any other micronational weapon will not be reconized by the Imperium. If said nation makes policy shifts from such behavior he may be reconized by the Imperium after three months of peace and friendship with the nations neighbors.<br>
<br>
If a nation is created by a rebel faction taking over the mother nations forums, or by said nation hijacking the nations boards it will not be reconized.  Reconigtion for such a nation will only occur if the mother nation reconizes the daughter nation.  If the split of is agreed by both parties peacefully and diplomatically then we may reconize the nation on a case by case basis.  Nations who put on a charade rebellion, revolution, or coup may be reconized as normal once they become stable. <br>
<br>
4. Recognition of a nation will be terminated automatically if the other nation stops recognition of our nation.  If a nation supports terrorist organizations or actions said nation will be dealt with by a vote in the conclave on a case by case basis to terminate relations.  If a nation attacks us it will automatically lose recognition from us.  If a nation supports or recognizes nations whom are formed through coups, rebellions, and unpopular uprising will be dealt with on a case by case basis in the Conclave.<br>
<br>
5. The types of recognition are as follows.  Friends, mutual recognition, and allies.  A friend is a nation who has not entered into a mutual recognition treaty but has began friendly diplomatic relations.  Mutual recognition is when both nations agree to reconize each other as a micro-nation.  Allies are nations who have entered into an alliance of any kind.<br>
<br>
<br>
Section III<br>
6. A foreign representative is a person who officially speaks on behalf of a their nation in Menelmacar. Menelmacar reserves the right to decline a foreign representative; all foreign representatives must be accepted by the Conclave of Equals.<br>
<br>
7. An ambassador is authorized to enter into friendly relations with another nation.  He is limited in that any mutual recognition, treaties must be passed through the Conclave of Equals.  His main purpose is to gather information, and cultural knowledge, and political affiliations of a nation, to present in the Foreign Edification forum to educate Menelmacari Citizens. An Ambassador may only offer comminque's pertaining to friendship, not mutual recognitions, or treaties.  <br>
<br>
Section IV<br>
8.  <br>
9. Menelmacar may not join any organization who's powers would extend over the Imperium of Menelmacar.  Menelmacar's status as a soveriegn micronation may not be threatened, or broken by any organization.  Organizations that do not affect Menelmacar's internal policy may be joined by vote in the Conclave of Equals<br>
<br>
10, 11, 12. Menelmacari Ambassadors if ever given admittance to Internal Organizations or major conventions may not act independetly.  They are simply a mouth piece of the people acting ont he peoples behalf.  They may not vote, or give Menelmacari endorsement on issues without Conclave approval<br>
<br>
Section V<br>
13. If a nation threatens Menelmacar, the Ambassador to the nation threatening may issue a protest on behalf of Menelmacar voicing it's dissproval of such actions.  The Ambassador may then propose in the Conclave th banning of Members from said nation until the threat subsides.  If a nation does not have a Menelmacari ambassador any citizen may propose to the Conclave the banning of citizens of the nation threatening Menelmacar until the thread subsides.<br>
<br>
If a nation attacks Menelmacari through hacking, cracking, or viruses the nations forums or citizen's e-mail account.  It is the responsibility of each citizen to report the actions of the criminals to macronational authority.  The nation responsibles entire population will be banned from Menelmacar until an investigation into the crimes is complete.  Citizens of attacking nation may be unbanned on a case by case basis.<br>
<br>
If a nation attacks Menelmacar through spamming, flooding, or ez board type bombs Menelmacar will simply delete said items from it Forum, and swiftly ban all citizens from the attacking nation until a complete investigation is performed to determine the exact culprit.  Upon determing the attackers those not involved may be unbanned on a case by case basis by the Conclave.  <br>
<br>
Menelmacar will not engage in warfare with a nation that violates macronational law, or violates EZ Boards Terms of service.  Menelmacar is a law abiding nation and will not engage in illegal behavior.<br>
<br>
14. <br>
If the assailnt of an Attack is unknown it is the duty of Menelmacari Police to inform the administrator of the attack for clean up, and to put Membership by Approval (MBA) on until the Conclave deems it safe to remove MBA.<br>
